	<h1 class="title">“黑色星期五”大促不再与你无关，你想买些啥？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/998/small/998.jpg?1402274915" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">唐云路</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2014-08-21 13:22:19 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/1966/medium/1966.jpg?1436647006" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


